msgid ""
"‘tāyapi kho tvaṃ, āvuso gotama, iriyāya tāya paṭipadāya tāya dukkarakārikāya "
"nājjhagamā uttari manussadhammā alamariyañāṇadassanavisesaṃ; kiṃ pana tvaṃ "
"etarahi bāhulliko padhānavibbhanto āvatto bāhullāya adhigamissasi uttari "
"manussadhammā alamariyañāṇadassanavisesan’ti?"
msgstr "‘Reverend Gotama … you’ve fallen into indulgence.’"

msgctxt "mn85:51.15"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho ahaṃ, rājakumāra, pañcavaggiye bhikkhū etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr "So for a second time I said to them:"

msgctxt "mn85:51.16"
msgid ""
"‘na, bhikkhave, tathāgato bāhulliko na padhānavibbhanto na āvatto bāhullāya."
msgstr "‘The Realized One has not become indulgent …’"

msgctxt "mn85:51.17"
msgid "Arahaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato sammāsambuddho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:51.18"
msgid ""
"Odahatha, bhikkhave, sotaṃ. Amatamadhigataṃ ahamanusāsāmi, ahaṃ dhammaṃ "
"desemi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:51.19"
msgid ""
"Yathānusiṭṭhaṃ tathā paṭipajjamānā nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā "
"sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissathā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc60"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:51.20"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho, rājakumāra, pañcavaggiyā bhikkhū maṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "But for a third time they said to me:"

msgctxt "mn85:51.21"
msgid ""
"‘tāyapi kho tvaṃ, āvuso gotama, iriyāya tāya paṭipadāya tāya dukkarakārikāya "
"nājjhagamā uttari manussadhammā alamariyañāṇadassanavisesaṃ; kiṃ pana tvaṃ "
"etarahi bāhulliko padhānavibbhanto āvatto bāhullāya adhigamissasi uttari "
"manussadhammā alamariyañāṇadassanavisesan’ti?"
msgstr "‘Reverend Gotama … you’ve fallen into indulgence.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya52"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc61"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:52.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, rājakumāra, pañcavaggiye bhikkhū etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr "So I said to them:"

#. VAR: pabhāvitametan’ti → vab­bhāvi­ta­metanti (bj) | bhāsitametanti (s1-3)
msgctxt "mn85:52.2"
msgid ""
"‘abhijānātha me no tumhe, bhikkhave, ito pubbe evarūpaṃ pabhāvitametan’ti?"
msgstr "‘Mendicants, have you ever known me to speak like this before?’"

msgctxt "mn85:52.3"
msgid "‘No hetaṃ, bhante’."
msgstr "‘No, sir.’"

msgctxt "mn85:52.4"
msgid "‘Arahaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato sammāsambuddho."
msgstr "‘The Realized One is Perfected, a fully awakened Buddha."

msgctxt "mn85:52.5"
msgid ""
"Odahatha, bhikkhave, sotaṃ. Amatamadhigataṃ ahamanusāsāmi, ahaṃ dhammaṃ "
"desemi."
msgstr ""
"Listen up, mendicants: I have achieved the Deathless! I shall instruct you, "
"I will teach you the Dhamma."

msgctxt "mn85:52.6"
msgid ""
"Yathānusiṭṭhaṃ tathā paṭipajjamānā nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā "
"sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissathā’ti."
msgstr ""
"By practicing as instructed you will soon realize the supreme end of the "
"spiritual path in this very life. You will live having achieved with your "
"own insight the goal for which people from good families rightly go forth "
"from the lay life to homelessness.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya53"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.94"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc62"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:53.1"
msgid "Asakkhiṃ kho ahaṃ, rājakumāra, pañcavaggiye bhikkhū saññāpetuṃ."
msgstr "I was able to persuade the group of five mendicants."

msgctxt "mn85:53.2"
msgid "Dvepi sudaṃ, rājakumāra, bhikkhū ovadāmi. Tayo bhikkhū piṇḍāya caranti."
msgstr ""
"Then sometimes I advised two mendicants, while the other three went for alms."

#. VAR: chabbaggiyā → chabbaggā (s1-3, km) | chabbaggo (pts1)
msgctxt "mn85:53.3"
msgid "Yaṃ tayo bhikkhū piṇḍāya caritvā āharanti, tena chabbaggiyā yāpema."
msgstr "Then those three would feed all six of us with what they brought back."

msgctxt "mn85:53.4"
msgid "Tayopi sudaṃ, rājakumāra, bhikkhū ovadāmi, dve bhikkhū piṇḍāya caranti."
msgstr ""
"Sometimes I advised three mendicants, while the other two went for alms."

msgctxt "mn85:53.5"
msgid "Yaṃ dve bhikkhū piṇḍāya caritvā āharanti tena chabbaggiyā yāpema."
msgstr "Then those two would feed all six of us with what they brought back."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya54"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc63"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:54.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, rājakumāra, pañcavaggiyā bhikkhū mayā evaṃ ovadiyamānā evaṃ "
"anusāsiyamānā nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā "
"anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme "
"sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihariṃsū”ti."
msgstr ""
"As the group of five mendicants were being advised and instructed by me like "
"this, they soon realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very "
"life. They lived having achieved with their own insight the goal for which "
"people from good families rightly go forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness.” "

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya55"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc64"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:55.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bodhi rājakumāro bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Prince Bodhi said to the Buddha:"

#. VAR: vināyakaṃ → nāyakaṃ (?)
msgctxt "mn85:55.2"
msgid ""
"“kīva cirena nu kho, bhante, bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ labhamāno—"
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, when a mendicant has the Realized One as trainer, how long would it "
"take for them to realize the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very "
"life?” "

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc65"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:55.3"
msgid ""
"“Tena hi, rājakumāra, taṃyevettha paṭipucchissāmi. Yathā te khameyya, tathā "
"naṃ byākareyyāsi."
msgstr ""
"“Well then, prince, I’ll ask you about this in return, and you can answer as "
"you like."

msgctxt "mn85:55.4"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rājakumāra, "
msgstr "What do you think, prince? "

#. VAR: aṅkusagayhe → aṅkusagaṇhe (s1-3, km)
#. VAR: hatthārūḷhe → hatthāruyhe (bj) | haṭṭhārūyhe (pts1)
msgctxt "mn85:55.5"
msgid "kusalo tvaṃ hatthārūḷhe aṅkusagayhe sippe”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Are you skilled in the art of wielding a hooked goad while riding an "
"elephant?”"

msgctxt "mn85:55.6"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante, kusalo ahaṃ hatthārūḷhe aṅkusagayhe sippe”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya56"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc66"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:56.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rājakumāra, "
msgstr "“What do you think, prince? "

msgctxt "mn85:56.2"
msgid "idha puriso āgaccheyya:"
msgstr "Suppose a man were to come along thinking:"

msgctxt "mn85:56.3"
msgid "‘bodhi rājakumāro hatthārūḷhaṃ aṅkusagayhaṃ sippaṃ jānāti;"
msgstr ""
"‘Prince Bodhi knows the art of wielding a hooked goad while riding an "
"elephant."

msgctxt "mn85:56.4"
msgid "tassāhaṃ santike hatthārūḷhaṃ aṅkusagayhaṃ sippaṃ sikkhissāmī’ti."
msgstr "I’ll train in that art under him.’"

msgctxt "mn85:56.5"
msgid "So cassa assaddho;"
msgstr "If he’s faithless,"

msgctxt "mn85:56.6"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ saddhena pattabbaṃ taṃ na sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he wouldn’t achieve what he could with faith."

msgctxt "mn85:56.7"
msgid "So cassa bahvābādho;"
msgstr "If he’s unhealthy,"

msgctxt "mn85:56.8"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ appābādhena pattabbaṃ taṃ na sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he wouldn’t achieve what he could with good health."

msgctxt "mn85:56.9"
msgid "So cassa saṭho māyāvī;"
msgstr "If he’s devious or deceitful,"

msgctxt "mn85:56.10"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ asaṭhena amāyāvinā pattabbaṃ taṃ na sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he wouldn’t achieve what he could with honesty and integrity."

msgctxt "mn85:56.11"
msgid "So cassa kusīto;"
msgstr "If he’s lazy,"

msgctxt "mn85:56.12"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ āraddhavīriyena pattabbaṃ taṃ na sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he wouldn’t achieve what he could with energy."

msgctxt "mn85:56.13"
msgid "So cassa duppañño;"
msgstr "If he’s stupid,"

msgctxt "mn85:56.14"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ paññavatā pattabbaṃ taṃ na sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he wouldn’t achieve what he could with wisdom."

msgctxt "mn85:56.15"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rājakumāra, "
msgstr "What do you think, prince? "

msgctxt "mn85:56.16"
msgid ""
"api nu so puriso tava santike hatthārūḷhaṃ aṅkusagayhaṃ sippaṃ sikkheyyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Could that man still train under you in the art of wielding a hooked goad "
"while riding an elephant?”"

msgctxt "mn85:56.17"
msgid ""
"“Ekamekenāpi, bhante, aṅgena samannāgato so puriso na mama santike "
"hatthārūḷhaṃ aṅkusagayhaṃ sippaṃ sikkheyya, ko pana vādo pañcahaṅgehī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, if he had even a single one of these factors he couldn’t train under "
"me, not to speak of all five.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya57"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.95"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc67"></a>
