msgstr "he’d achieve what he could with good health."

msgctxt "mn85:57.9"
msgid "So cassa asaṭho amāyāvī;"
msgstr "If he’s honest and has integrity,"

msgctxt "mn85:57.10"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ asaṭhena amāyāvinā pattabbaṃ taṃ sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he’d achieve what he could with honesty and integrity."

msgctxt "mn85:57.11"
msgid "So cassa āraddhavīriyo;"
msgstr "If he’s energetic,"

msgctxt "mn85:57.12"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ āraddhavīriyena pattabbaṃ taṃ sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he’d achieve what he could with energy."

msgctxt "mn85:57.13"
msgid "So cassa paññavā;"
msgstr "If he’s wise,"

msgctxt "mn85:57.14"
msgid "yāvatakaṃ paññavatā pattabbaṃ taṃ sampāpuṇeyya."
msgstr "he’d achieve what he could with wisdom."

msgctxt "mn85:57.15"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rājakumāra, "
msgstr "What do you think, prince? "

msgctxt "mn85:57.16"
msgid ""
"api nu so puriso tava santike hatthārūḷhaṃ aṅkusagayhaṃ sippaṃ sikkheyyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Could that man still train under you in the art of wielding a hooked goad "
"while riding an elephant?”"

