"not to speak of all five.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya58"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc68"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:58.1"
msgid "“Evameva kho, rājakumāra, pañcimāni padhāniyaṅgāni."
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, prince, there are these five factors that support "
"meditation."

msgctxt "mn85:58.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "mn85:58.3"
msgid "Idha, rājakumāra, bhikkhu saddho hoti; saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ:"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has faith in the Realized One’s awakening:"

msgctxt "mn85:58.4"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti;"
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "mn85:58.5"
msgid ""
"appābādho hoti appātaṅko samavepākiniyā gahaṇiyā samannāgato nātisītāya "
"nāccuṇhāya majjhimāya padhānakkhamāya;"
msgstr ""
"They are rarely ill or unwell. Their stomach digests well, being neither too "
"hot nor too cold, but just right, and fit for meditation."

msgctxt "mn85:58.6"
msgid ""
"asaṭho hoti amāyāvī yathābhūtaṃ attānaṃ āvikattā satthari vā viññūsu vā "
"sabrahmacārīsu;"
msgstr ""
"They’re not devious or deceitful. They reveal themselves honestly to the "
"Teacher or sensible spiritual companions."

msgctxt "mn85:58.7"
msgid ""
"āraddhavīriyo viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo anikkhittadhuro kusalesu dhammesu;"
msgstr ""
"They live with energy roused up for giving up unskillful qualities and "
"gaining skillful qualities. They’re strong, staunchly vigorous, not slacking "
"off when it comes to developing skillful qualities."

msgctxt "mn85:58.8"
msgid ""
"paññavā hoti udayatthagāminiyā paññāya samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya "
"sammādukkhakkhayagāminiyā."
msgstr ""
"They’re wise. They have the wisdom of arising and passing away which is "
"noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending of suffering."

msgctxt "mn85:58.9"
msgid "Imāni kho, rājakumāra, pañca padhāniyaṅgāni."
msgstr "These are the five factors that support meditation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya59"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.96"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc69"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:59.1"
msgid ""
"Imehi, rājakumāra, pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ "
"vināyakaṃ labhamāno—"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant with these five factors that support meditation has the "
"Realized One as trainer, they could"

msgctxt "mn85:59.2"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyya satta vassāni."
msgstr "realize the supreme end of the spiritual path in seven years."

msgctxt "mn85:59.3"
msgid "Tiṭṭhantu, rājakumāra, satta vassāni."
msgstr "Let alone seven years,"

msgctxt "mn85:59.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ "
"labhamāno—"
msgstr "they could"

msgctxt "mn85:59.5"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyya chabbassāni …"
msgstr "realize the supreme end of the spiritual path in six years,"

msgctxt "mn85:59.6"
msgid "pañca vassāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.7"
msgid "cattāri vassāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.8"
msgid "tīṇi vassāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.9"
msgid "dve vassāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.10"
msgid "ekaṃ vassaṃ."
msgstr "or as little as one year."

msgctxt "mn85:59.11"
msgid "Tiṭṭhatu, rājakumāra, ekaṃ vassaṃ."
msgstr "Let alone one year,"

msgctxt "mn85:59.12"
msgid ""
"Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ "
"labhamāno—"
msgstr ""
"when a mendicant with these five factors that support meditation has the "
"Realized One as trainer, they could"

msgctxt "mn85:59.13"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyya satta māsāni."
msgstr "realize the supreme end of the spiritual path in seven months,"

msgctxt "mn85:59.14"
msgid "Tiṭṭhantu, rājakumāra, satta māsāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.15"
msgid ""
"Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ "
"labhamāno—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.16"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.17"
msgid ""
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyya cha māsāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.18"
msgid "pañca māsāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.19"
msgid "cattāri māsāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.20"
msgid "tīṇi māsāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.21"
msgid "dve māsāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.22"
msgid "ekaṃ māsaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.23"
msgid "aḍḍhamāsaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.24"
msgid "Tiṭṭhatu, rājakumāra, aḍḍhamāso."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.25"
msgid ""
"Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ "
"labhamāno—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.26"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.27"
msgid ""
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyya satta rattindivāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.28"
msgid "Tiṭṭhantu, rājakumāra, satta rattindivāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.29"
msgid ""
"Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ "
"labhamāno—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.30"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.31"
msgid ""
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyya cha rattindivāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.32"
msgid "pañca rattindivāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.33"
msgid "cattāri rattindivāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.34"
msgid "tīṇi rattindivāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.35"
msgid "dve rattindivāni …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:59.36"
msgid "ekaṃ rattindivaṃ."
msgstr "or as little as one day."

msgctxt "mn85:59.37"
msgid "Tiṭṭhatu, rājakumāra, eko rattindivo."
msgstr "Let alone one day,"

msgctxt "mn85:59.38"
msgid ""
"Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ "
"labhamāno sāyamanusiṭṭho pāto visesaṃ adhigamissati, pātamanusiṭṭho sāyaṃ "
"visesaṃ adhigamissatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"when a mendicant with these five factors that support meditation has the "
"Realized One as trainer, they could be instructed in the evening and achieve "
"distinction in the morning, or be instructed in the morning and achieve "
"distinction in the evening.”"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya60"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:60.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bodhi rājakumāro bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Prince Bodhi said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "mn85:60.2"
msgid "“aho buddho, aho dhammo, aho dhammassa svākkhātatā."
msgstr ""
"“Oh, the Buddha! Oh, the teaching! Oh, how well explained is the teaching!"

msgctxt "mn85:60.3"
msgid ""
"Yatra hi nāma sāyamanusiṭṭho pāto visesaṃ adhigamissati, pātamanusiṭṭho "
"sāyaṃ visesaṃ adhigamissatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"For someone could be instructed in the evening and achieve distinction in "
"the morning, or be instructed in the morning and achieve distinction in the "
"evening.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya61"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.97"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc70"></a>
msgctxt "mn85:61.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, sañjikāputto māṇavo bodhiṃ rājakumāraṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Sañjikāputta said to Prince Bodhi:"

msgctxt "mn85:61.2"
msgid "“evameva panāyaṃ bhavaṃ bodhi:"
msgstr "“Though Master Bodhi speaks like this,"

#. VAR: vadeti → vadesi (si) | pavedeti (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn85:61.3"
msgid "‘aho buddho, aho dhammo, aho dhammassa svākkhātatā’ti ca vadeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn85:61.4"
msgid ""
"atha ca pana na taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati dhammañca "
"bhikkhusaṃghañcā”ti."
msgstr ""
"you don’t go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the "
"mendicant Saṅgha.”"

msgctxt "mn85:61.5"
msgid ""
"“Mā hevaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, avaca; mā hevaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, avaca."
msgstr "“Don’t say that, dear Sañjikāputta, don’t say that."

# Quotes in MS are incorrect.
msgctxt "mn85:61.6"
msgid ""
"Sammukhā metaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, ayyāya sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ”."
msgstr "I have heard and learned this in the presence of the lady, my mother."

msgctxt "mn85:61.7"
msgid ""
"“Ekamidaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati "
"ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"This one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery."

msgctxt "mn85:61.8"
msgid ""
"Atha kho me ayyā kucchimatī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho me ayyā "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then my pregnant mother went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "mn85:61.9"
msgid ""
"‘yo me ayaṃ, bhante, kucchigato kumārako vā kumārikā vā so bhagavantaṃ "
"saraṇaṃ gacchati dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, the prince or princess in my womb goes for refuge to the Buddha, the "
"teaching, and the mendicant Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn85:61.10"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ taṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan’ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember them as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.’"

msgctxt "mn85:61.11"
msgid ""
"Ekamidaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, samayaṃ bhagavā idheva bhaggesu viharati "
"susumāragire bhesakaḷāvane migadāye."
msgstr ""
"Another time the Buddha was staying here in the land of the Bhaggas on "
"Crocodile Hill, in the deer park at Bhesakaḷā’s Wood."

msgctxt "mn85:61.12"
msgid ""
"Atha kho maṃ dhāti aṅkena haritvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho maṃ dhāti "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then my nurse, carrying me on her hip, went to the Buddha, bowed, stood to "
"one side, and said to him:"

msgctxt "mn85:61.13"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ, bhante, bodhi rājakumāro bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati dhammañca "
"bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, this Prince Bodhi goes for refuge to the Buddha, to the teaching, and "
"to the mendicant Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn85:61.14"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ taṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan’ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember him as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.’"

msgctxt "mn85:61.15"
msgid ""
"Esāhaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, tatiyakampi bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi "
"dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""
"Now for a third time I go for refuge to the Buddha, to the teaching, and to "
"the mendicant Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn85:61.16"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn85:61.17"
msgid "Bodhirājakumārasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
